English.Text: "Clever. Very clever," admits the medal-draped governor, as he puffs solemnly on his cigar. "How did you know the innkeeper was my brother?" Your emissary doesn't let slip it was pure guesswork. "Go ahead, take whatever you want," he gestures to a warehouse bursting with confiscated goods, "so long as you keep quiet about all thisâ€” can't have my superiors finding out."
